node.text: #WeThriveInside from the Child Mind Institute is a comprehensive source of mental health support for families during the COVID-19 crisis. We are all struggling to cope with isolation, anxiety and fear. The Child Mind Institute is an essential source of information, insight, and clinical care via telehealth services to help families navigate these challenging times. For resources or to donate please visit @childmind.org

node.text: @beyonce our friendship has evolved so much over the years. Life gets in the way sometimes; family, kids, career, etc. While we don’t see each other as much day to day as we used to, it’s beautiful that we can still collaborate artistically on such important pieces of work such as this. We don’t say it enough to each other, but you mean a lot to me 💖

node.text:
Working with family can be complicated. But working with my daughter Fig was a breeze. Besides her obvious good looks, her on set demeanor was one I was incredibly proud of. You never cease to amaze me baby. Fatherhood is complicated and I won’t always have the right answers, but luckily you seem to always find your way. They grow up fast don’t they?

@gq @gqstyle
